getEnumByValue(int) - Static method in enum de.drsilence.irclib.IrcReplies
Searches for a known enum-representiv for a given IRC error/reply number.
Replies are only RFC1459 codes and ERR_NOTDEFINED can be used to handle costume replies.
getErrorCode() - Method in enum de.drsilence.irclib.IrcReplies
Returns IRC1459 error/reply code of this Enum.
getErrorString() - Method in enum de.drsilence.irclib.IrcReplies
Returns IRC1459 error/reply message.
